Package main

Class GenerateRandom

java.lang.Object
main.GenerateRandom
public class GenerateRandom extends Object
The GenerateRandom class provides functionality for generating random objects such as Athletes, Items, and Teams. It uses randomisation to create dynamic elements for the game.
Author:
Yunu Cho, Kush Desai
